snippet.title: Zack Zero Steam Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
ZACK ZERO IS NOW AVAILABLE ON STEAM
http://store.steampowered.com/app/234290

SPECIAL PROMOTION! Offer ends 13 May
The award-winning action-platform game is now available for only €7,49/GB £5.24/US $7.49, a special release offer with a 25% discount on the official price of €9,99/GB £6.99/US $9.99. The new and improved PC version includes HD graphics, enhanced textures and effects, new animations, new levels and improved player experience. 

http://www.zackzero.com

©2013 Crocodile Entertainment
